sultants in providing enterprise-wide solutions,&quot; Ruffolo said.andO;&quot;The programs will enable NCR and its partners to mutually benefit frombusiness opportunities across a variety of targeted customer environments andkey industry segments.&quot;andO;</TEXT></DOC>